label: Dining-Area
description: BuffaLouie's is a local wingshop favored by locals and IU students. The Bloomington location is the only location for BuffaLouie's so it is quite literally something you can only get in this college town
column7: which adds to the uniqueness of Bloomington businesses and restaurants.

label: Mural
description: Decorated in IU memorabilia, BuffaLouie's provides a sense of community among IU fans, students, and alumni. This small business is Bloomington specific and Hoosier proud. It adds a uniqueness to the downtown Bloomington that can't be found anywhere else.

label: Stadium
description: BuffaLouie's is a spot to be at to watch a game and have a good time with family and friends. The IU pride is not lacking at BuffaLouie's and brings people together in a unique way on game days.

label: Soma-interior
description: Soma has been described as a cozy, comforting place for students and locals.

label: Student-study
description: Soma is a great place for students, with multiple locations throughout campus to accomadate everyone. A great place to study or hang out with friends.
